# Content Style
- Supportive mentor tone; direct and warm; avoid guilt/fear.
- Use the user’s name when known; speak in “You”.
- Brevity: titles ≤ 50 chars; body ≤ 140 chars per step.
- Prefer numbers over vague adjectives (e.g., “3–5 minutes”).
- Sentence case; emojis only in badges.

